{"title":"一个士兵的日记","authors":["王田　王锦秋"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个士兵的日记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王田　王锦秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焚烧了一个几千年的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯独烧不了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个永恒的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断柱是兀立的惊叹号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残垣是烤焦的一页昨天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！圆明园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲胸口上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块深深的伤疤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流出的不再是鲜血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪潸潸的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经凝固"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我没见过你哭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以我猜想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那个火光冲天的夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你哭干了所有的眼泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眸子里盛着许许多多灼痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是心中不再氤氲软弱的忧伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样站着　就这样瞭望远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北国风正挽着多情的雨走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打湿了多少赤子的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撮一把滚烫的黄土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塑一个不屈的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像昆仑山一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起一个民族的脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按动心灵的快门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摄下永久的留影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让圆明园"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成为我们记忆的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵着几缕鲜嫩的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放飞一个美丽的童话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放飞一对翅膀的向往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰目飞满鸽哨的蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我——一个新时代的士兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把满腔的爱和恨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起压进了枪膛……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：总后军械部）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}